text: First year ke time tera GPL ke vakt reaction ek taraf aur uske baad tune jitni bhi bakchodiyan (HEC, robotics, korea, jaguar, aur bhi h kaafi) ki vo ek taraf. Alag level change aaya bhai tere me. Teri wajah se koi to tha jo wing me mere se chhota tha ğŸ˜†. All the best tere startup ke liye yr. Milte h jald hi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: Yaad h teri cycle pe haath cross karke chalane vaali baat.. jiske vajah se mera saath kaand ho gya tha. Usse mujhe sabak mila aise stunts sabke bas ki baat nahi h ğŸ˜†. Tu almost har mahine me ek baar to lucknow chal hi jaata tha na.. par kabhi kuch tips nahi mili yr ğŸ˜¢. Vo judgement ya koi bhi random patton ke game ki nights me kitna maja aata tha yr. Vapas milte h yr jald hi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
First sem se apan ki baatein shayad psychology ke course se start hui thi. Kaise apan humesha presentation just ek raat pehle banane CC jaate the aur itni baar apni turn next week postpone hone par bhi humesha next week ki ek raat pehle hi har baar CC jaate the ğŸ˜†. Ladkiyon se tu ghira rehta tha humesha aur wing vaalon ko mera magnetic field batata tha saale.
Teri humesha sabko pagal banane ki vajah se main believe nahi kar rha tha ki tujhe sach me corona ho gya tha. Bhediye vaali kahaani real life me dekh li thi us din.
Summer me FIFA aur NFS me kitna maja aaya tha yr. Kitni movies dekhi yr saath mein mainly horror jisme Hitesh ke humesha maje lete the. Kaise kai baar apan ne ek dum instant movie plans banaye. Ek baar to sirf McD jaane ke liye apan ne Mission Mangal ka plan bana liya ğŸ˜†. Aise hi koi trip ka plan banate h na corona ke baad.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
Tujhe main sabse jyada daring banda maanta hu main yr abhi tak jisse bhi mila hu. Koi bhi baat ho bilkul load nahi leta yr tu.. itna easily aur itne acche se handle kar leta h jo situations sun ke bhi fatti h meri. Vo daring chahiye yr life me. Tera naam Bahubali perfectly suit karta h tujhe.
Agar kuch bhi baat chal rahi ho us par instant replies hote the jisme tu koshish karta h funny hone ka.. vo bhi kabhi kabhi sahi me funny hote h ğŸ™ƒ.  
Yaad h vo swimming pool vaali jab summer me jaate the ğŸ˜†. Vo mili kya kabhi ya conclude kar liya tha ki vo Anshuman vaali thi. Aur accha hua main teri vaali bus ke liye wait nahi kiya at the end as vo cancel ho gayi thi ğŸ˜†. Kabhi future me meri kisi se ladai ho to bacha lena yr apne chacha se bol kar. â€œGhar pe pta chalta to 6 ki 6 utaar deteâ€: Bhand Bahubali ğŸ˜†. 
Better half se baat kaise karata saale kyunki sabki nahi hoti laxman ğŸ˜¢. Aur darega tu.. jab teri vaali mujhpe phisal jayegi ğŸ˜›.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
Yaad h apni first time baat college aane se bhi pehle hui thi. Mujhe kaafi confusion tha college choose karne ka to mere dost (who knew you through brilliant) ne tera number diya tha as tera shayad confirm tha IITK aane ka. Really uss time bilkul nahi socha tha ki us ek call se apna ek permanent connection jud jayega ğŸ˜„. Sahi me yr iske baad apan ko same hall milne ke hi itne kam chances the.. apan ko to wing tak same mil gayi ğŸ˜†. Aur fir har course me same team ğŸ˜†.

Aur ha, kya be saale kuch bhi random baat pe shart kaun rakhta h ğŸ˜† par ha vo to h ki kaafi baar tere predictions sahi ho jaate the ğŸ˜†. Obviously including wing vaali bakchodiyan apan ne kaafi saari cheezein saath me hi ki h na college me like DEs and even random OEs and ESOs bhi, summer project jisme mera guest lecture tha ğŸ˜›, ICPC regionals. Par sahi me yr tere saath itna close rehke itna kuch seekha hoon na yr main personality aur technicality wise dono ki life me vapas kab aisa mauka milega pta nahi. Aisi kripa aage bhi barsaate rehna.

Story pe reply jaisi aur bhi tips aage bhi jaroor dete rehna.. kuch  bhala humara bhi ho jaye ğŸ˜. Aur aise hi reels share karte rehna. Sahi h yr exercise karke fit hoja aur stamina badha le ğŸ˜› fir ek bandi patana jiski best friend single ho ğŸ˜†.
Baat rahi assignments ki to shayad tu likhte vakt bhand tha ğŸ˜† kyunki yaad kar humesha tune bachaya h mujhe. Dekha ro diya na yahan bhi ğŸ˜›.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: C-205 ya uske saamne vaale bed par pade hue tu clash of clans ke baare me gyan pelta rehta tha ğŸ˜†. Mujhe first time insta chalana aur uspe stalk maarna tune hi sikhaya h. Teri kahaniyaan (like vo inter IIT ka pura safar) epic hoti thi yr.. aur kaafi jyada super detailed bhi ğŸ˜†. Milte hain yr vapas jaldi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: Bhai kitna multi talented insaan h tu.. taekwondo, fine arts, badminton, basketball sab me chaapu. Tu bhi panda ki tarah koi bhi movie dekhne jaana ho humesha ready rehta tha chahe kaisi bhi movie ho ğŸ˜†. Teri art ke baare me suna tha bas shayad maine first year me. Tujhe galaxy me fine arts me live karta dekh ke jo feel aayi thi na bhai alag level thi. Aur yaad kar tera naya naam pari bhi galaxy ke dinon se hi originate hua tha ğŸ˜†. Uske baad se aaj tak puri wing ne jo maje liye tere aur aage bhi lete rahenge ğŸ˜†. Chal milte h vapas kabhi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: Tere se baat karke humesha energetic aur maturity vaali vibes aati thi which makes you a really nice person to talk with anytime. Aur accha hua tera one of the best buddy Ashu mere next room me tha.. jisse apni lectures ke alawa bhi baat ho jaati thi ğŸ˜†. Milte h yr vapas kabhi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: First year me galaxy me har raat ko jaake backdrops banane (ya bigadne?) ke time apan ne shayad first time jyada baat kari hogi. Jis din result aaya tha us din sabke saath milkar judge ko gariya rahe the ğŸ˜†. Mujhe ye humesha pakka hota tha ki koi aur DEs dekhne jaaye ya na jaye tu humesha chalega saath. Chahe vo DEs ho ya antaragni ya galaxy, ek bhi dance miss nahi karte the apan ğŸ˜†. Teri English humesha yaad rahegi yr. Milte h jaldi.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: One of the most rone vaala banda I ever met but hamesha at the end chaapne vaala. Jab main final sem campus vaapas aaya tab tujhe dekhke confidence aaya ki chalo main akela nahi phoola ğŸ˜†. Accha hua tune vapas aane ka flight se karaya varna agar bus se karata aur vikram book karta to vo tujhe pakka dobara ditch maar deta ğŸ˜†. Chal milte h jaldi aur mini militia khelte h.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
Shuru me jab tujhe dekha tha lagta tha ki iske saath kabhi panga le liya to g**nd maar lega ğŸ˜†. Par jab baat kari to pta chala ki haathi ke daant dikhane ke aur khane ke aur. Uske baad kisi ko personality wise judge nahi kiya hoga maine ğŸ˜†. Itna jyada caring dost nahi dekha hoga yr maine pehle.
Agar GLY101 ka course nahi karta to main aaj bhi vahi Sarthak rah jaata to college aane se pehle tha. Apan ko ek petition daalni chaiye yr ki atleast hall level par HECs GLY implement kare ğŸ˜†. Ha yr first year par tere room par kuch bhi bakchodiyan maarte rehte the aur Devashish ke maje lete rehte the.
Apan dono ka combo best hota tha yr humesha doosro ki maarne ke liye. Koi bhi aajao fir to saala le hi lenge uski aisa tha ğŸ˜†. Ek baar apan ne mere room pe lights out kya dekh li uske baad Diana ki maarne vaala joke to permanent tha.
Tere se jyada health conscious banda nahi dekha yr maine which is really good yr. Kabhi keto kabhi gym na unfit honge hum. Aage kabhi bhi fitness tips leni hogi to google karne se pehle tujhe call karunga.
Chal theek h yr log blood donate karte h which is good par blood bahar nikalne ke liye pet me sariya kaun ghuswata h bhai ğŸ˜†. Dhyaan rakhna aisi bakchodiyan kam karna ho sake to.
Apne startup ke ideas humesha sunate rehna aur thoda trading aur finance ka bhi gyan dete rehna. Ha yr trip karni hi h corona khatam hote hi. Aur ha bhoolte usko h jisko dimaag me yaad rakhne ki jarurat ho.. usko nahi jo dil me h (thoda fimly ho gya shayad).
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
Maine bohot koshish par mujhe bilkul yaad nahi aa rha apni baat start kaise hui thi. Shayad apan itni easily ghul mil gye ki vo starting point identify karna easy nahi h ğŸ˜†. Yaar teri jaisi sincerity aur attitude agar poori duniya me hoti to aaj jitne negative factors h duniya me shayad vo na hote. Tere so jo vibes nikalti h na usse koi Aman jaisa banda bhi aalas na kare ğŸ˜†. Sahi me agar tu nahi hota to kaafi baar apan cheezein/plannings start bhi nahi kar paate.

Yaad h apan jab bhi koi movie dekhne vaale hote the to movie se jyada time ye dekhne me laga dete the ki movie dekhni kaunsi h ğŸ˜†. Yr thodi aisi harkatein aur karte agar tera campus vapas aana possible ho paata. Par koi na milte hain kabhi aur dekhte hain â€œmoviesâ€ + karte h >=1 trip(s).

Aur tu baakiyon ke saath single hone par kyun rota tha be. Abhi se to rishte aane lag gaye tere liye ğŸ˜†. Ye to vahi vaali baat ho gayi ki inke haath me sone ka katora dedoge fir bhi ye bheekh maangenge. Ek baar tu shuru karega to 10 aa jayengi.. jisme se ek idhar bhi paas kar dena ğŸ˜›.

Aaj bhi aur aage bhi tujhe pata h mujhse koi movies ya series ka puchne ka koi 
fayda nahi hai tereko. Humesha super set hi rahega tera ğŸ˜†. I think kuch hi log honge bas jinse tu le sakta h recommendations. Aur tune jaise kaha main tere aur uske baare me nahi likh raha, but I know koi na koi to likh hi dega ğŸ˜†.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text:
Ha yr apan first half me mile hi nahi jyada.. pta nahi kaise. Iss saale corona ke chakkar me bhi second half ka aadha portion aise hi nikal gya. Mujhe jahan tak yaad h apan first time baat kiye the jab tune vo dosa vaala kaand kiya tha aur tujhe train ke liye late ho rha tha. Tab apan meri cycle par gaye the gate tak tujhe chhorne (kuch ha**miyon ke vajah se â€˜râ€™ use kiya varna hamesha â€˜dâ€™ use karta hu ğŸ˜…). Khair aise kitne kaand kiye h tune jisse sab log kaafi cheezein seekhte rahe ğŸ˜† ki kya kya nahi karna h life me ğŸ˜†.

Mujhe lagta h aise kaand karenge sab log hi but life me jitni jaldi kardo utna better h ğŸ˜†. Par maine dekha h tujhe un cases se kaafi seekhte hue jisse tere aage ke decisions definitely kaafi jyada rationale honge. Jo teri cheezon ko jaanne ki ultimate curiosity h na vo kabhi khatam mat hone dena yr.. chahe vo internet speed ko 1Gbps le jaane ki baat ho ya fir swap jaldi bharna start hone ko rokne ki. Aur apne dabbe me 50+ chrome tabs kholne ke liye try karte rehna ğŸ˜†. Aur bhi koi nayi bakchodi aaye dimaag me aage jaake to humesha batana mujhe bhi.

Parallel me kitni bandiyon se flirt karta hai be tu vo bhi kuch to bilkul random. Kabhi hume bhi sikha dete bhaiya aaj ye din nahi dekhne padte ğŸ˜¢. Insta pe stalk maarte hue koi mile to jaroor batana ğŸ˜›.

Also thanks for motivating me jab bhi I felt under-confident. And at last tu shayad â€œthinking aboutâ€ lagana bhool gaya â€œkeepâ€ ke baad in â€œI hope we will keep creating the PRs togetherâ€¦â€ ğŸ˜†. Aur PR request daalni h ya PR? ğŸ˜›
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: Aur bhai IITK ke chess god. Tere se jyada fraudy insaan nahi dekha yr. Par fraud maar ke bhi saare kaam complete kar leta tha ya karwa leta tha ğŸ˜›. Kabhi bhi movie dekhne jaana ho to koi aur ho na ho tu to humesha ready rehta tha chahe War jaise movie kyun na ho ğŸ˜†. Par lion king ke time dekh liya bhai order karne ki line me kabhi tereko aage nahi rakhna h. Saale sab ke liye coke ki itni badi baalti kaun order karta h be ğŸ˜†. Vo codechef vaala kaand yaad h.. Uske baad maine shayad hi kisi ko code bheja hoga ğŸ˜†. Milte h vapas yr kaafi time ho gya ab to.
author: Sarthak  Singhal

text: Bhai tere se jyada tech ka keeda kisi me nahi hoga. Tune shayad apna naya laptop bhi khol diya tha na ya purana vaala hi tha vo.  Asli engineer to tu ban rha h jo bhi mile usse khol deta h ğŸ˜†. And even first year me to khulwa bhi liya tha Barsaiyaan ki. Pure Y17 me akela banda hoga jisne senior ki khulwayi ho ğŸ˜†. Aur haan jab bhi milenge aur mera laptop saath me hoga to please force shut down mat maar dena agar white screen dikhe to ğŸ˜†.

text: Bindaas aadmi h yr tu vaise hi rehna humesha. Aur kya be saale desh drohi kaise.. kuch bhi? Tere vo ajeeb se situational questions puchna dobara milte h jab bhi.
